{"tid":157890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(薩德)韓國比台灣慘！限韓令600萬陸客蒸發","createTime":"2017-03-15T23:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T13:36:56.000Z","uid":35790,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3c36bdccf4462f3e02d927575b1493b68d473b","tid":157890,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T23:48:29.000Z","msg":"韓國比台灣慘！限韓令600萬陸客蒸發<br />\n<br />\n2017/03/16 07:04&nbsp;2117<br />\n<br />\n韓國不顧中國強烈反對，執意部署「薩德」（飛彈防禦系統），中國祭出「限韓令」，昨起生效。今日出刊的《中國時報》報導，中國國家旅遊局下令，自今年3月15日起，禁止旅行社組織、推廣韓國旅行團。<br />\n<br />\n業界估計，陸客赴韓將蒸發最多600萬人次，大減7成；每月4400多班中國飛往韓國的航班，恐面臨腰斬。大韓航空宣布，即日起至4月23日，針對8條中國客源不足的航線減班79班次；韓亞航空也在4月30日前，針對12條中國航線減班90班次。陸客不來，韓國消費總額大減近百億美元，免稅店首當其衝。估計若陸客減半持續1年，免稅店銷售額將損失4.3兆韓圜（約1100億台幣）。<br />\n（王嘉慶／綜合報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170316/1077372/1/韓國比台灣慘！限韓令　600萬陸客蒸發\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170316%2F1077372%2F1%2F%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%AF%94%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%85%98%EF%BC%81%E9%99%90%E9%9F%93%E4%BB%A4%E3%80%80600%E8%90%AC%E9%99%B8%E5%AE%A2%E8%92%B8%E7%99%BC&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evjy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=2af754ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170316/1077372/1/韓國比台灣慘！限韓令　600萬陸客蒸發</a>"},{"pid":"cb77fad2f578e2535d2e50ea3c51a5a27a8cf94a","tid":157890,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T23:49:57.000Z","msg":"幾時到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d5a86496b4281f77af81c543a94828bb59610f","tid":157890,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T23:50:25.000Z","msg":"一年唔去？<br />\n咁睇得起佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32dd8fd79650a4b1d865bf0206194d558b50d001","tid":157890,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T23:50:27.000Z","msg":